{
  "texts": [
    "The spatial constraint is learned from the 3D model of the target.",
    "When the target is occluded, view-specific DCFs are used to robustly localize the target.",
    "Camplani et al. [46] improved the CF method for scale estimation and occlusion handling in real time.Deep learning (DL).",
    "CNN is widely used in the tracking task because of its discriminative ability in feature representation.",
    "Various networks provide a powerful alternative to the traditional hand-crafted feature, which is the simplest way to utilize CNN."
  ]
}